title: South Korea : e-commerce sales volume 2009 to 2018
yAxis: E-commerce sales volume in trillion Korean won
summary: This line chart has an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing E-commerce sales volume in trillion Korean won with a total of 10 data points. The chart has one significant trend.
This trend is positive which exists from 2018 to 2009.
gold: This timeline shows online shopping transaction volume in South Korea from 2009 to 2018 . In 2018 , the online shopping transactions totaled more than 113 trillion South Korean won , up from around 92 trillion won in the previous year .
